 <description>&lt;p&gt;Cleber Gouv&amp;ecirc;a puxou assunto na lista sobre teoria da evolu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2012/06/a-perfect-and-beautiful-machine-what-darwins-theory-of-evolution-reveals-about-artificial-intelligence/258829/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;intelig&amp;ecirc;ncia artificial&lt;/a&gt;. Felipe Fonseca seguiu a conversa, questionando e &lt;a href=&quot;http://http://www.wired.com/beyond_the_beyond/2012/06/turing-centenary-speech-new-aesthetic/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;linkando outro texto&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
